<http://www.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/event/276AMGMBCQGDRLCCBKHTBVTLSLLQJBGBG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "SJTC: Mamma Mia!";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Mamma Mia</h1><span><br/></span>Music and Lyrics by Benny Andersson & Björn Ulvaeus and some songs with Stig Anderson<span><br/></span>Book by Catherine Johnson<span><br/></span>Originally conceived by Judy Craymer<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Performances</h2><span><br/></span><ul><li>Wednesday, May 20, 2026 at 7:30pm</li><li>Thursday, May 21, 2026 at 7:30pm</li><li>Friday, May 22, 2026 at 7:30pm</li><li>Saturday, May 23, 2026 at 2:00pm</li><li>Saturday, May 23, 2026 at 7:30pm</li><li>Sunday, May 24, 2026 at 2:00pm</li></ul><span><br/></span>Here we go again! Dance and sing along as we celebrate our 100th production at Imperial Theatre with Mamma Mia! This is your chance to experience one of our top-selling shows of all time. Join us for a show packed full of fun, laughter, and unforgettable music.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Purchase a <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://purchase.imperialtheatre.ca/FixedSeries\">SJTC Subscription</a> and save 30% off single ticket prices! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>We are happy to hold prior season subscribers' seats until September 2. Single tickets on sale September 2, 2025.
""";
